Tobitachem pustok mhollear eka ghorabeacher atthaploli kanni.  Nineveh xarant Tobit nanvancho ek mois jietalo.  Tachea Naftali kulla soit taka nirvaxit kelolo.  Tobit ek Devbhiranticho monis aslolean somurt palltalo, gorjevontank pavtalo ani atam to kudd'ddo zalolo.   Ekbatana ganvant tacho soiro Raguel ravtalo.  Sara, Raguelache dhuveche satui nhovre eka  fattlean ek korun lognananche ratich Asmodeus devcharan jivexim marlole.  Atam Tobit ani Sara apnnancher moronn dhadd mhonn Deva lagim magtat punn Dev tanchem magnnem aikota ani Apnnank zai te porim zap dita.  Dev aplea duta Rafaelak dhaddta zo Tobias hea Tobitachea putak Raguela-xim surokxitponnim haddta, take Sara lagim logn korta ni tachea Bapaicehm kudd'ddeponn borem korunk vokhod dita.  Hi ek dekhivont kanni, zoim bhik diupant animeloleam sovem karia pallpant khun nett ghatla.  Nia fhorabeachem jivit hantunt bhes bore torem vornnilam.  Lognanchi purnntai, kristi xikovnnent asa  mhonn dakhoilam.  Deivik boreponnanchi prokasnni Rafael duta vorvim Dev kollit korta.  dor disa hi Devachi kurpa amche thaim asa mhonn Tobitachem pustok amkam xikoita.  Tobitachem Pustok sumar 200 vorsam Kristi Xoka adim boroilolem-xem dista, chodd korun Palestina desant ani ghoddie Aramaik bhaxen.

